        <num>CC 637</num>
        <heading>637.  Nontransferable and nonheritable right</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 637.  Nontransferable and nonheritable right.
The right of habitation is neither transferable nor heritable.  It may not be alienated, let, or encumbered.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
